snippet.title: Heartland Season 15 Episode 8 Trailer - Tim is Leaving - Another Death in Heartland
snippet.description:
We are entering into December, meaning that there are only a few episodes of Heartland Season 15 left for us to explore. It is a shame, of course, since we cannot stand being left without Heartland. However, it is also good news because we know that Heartland keeps its best episodes towards the end of a season. Therefore, we are sure that the upcoming episodes will all be top-notch, keeping us all at the edge of our seats. In the previous episode, we felt major deja vu since we watched Amy struggling with the loss of Ty once again. This struggle was the constant theme of Season 14, which is the only season of Heartland that the fandom collectively disliked.
